PreSale.buyTokensByReferrer (/unique_chucks/15/0xbe138bb17d09a96166024e3f5b5cdff4c91d55dd.sol#190-198) sends eth to arbitrary user
	Dangerous calls:
	- holder.transfer(OPERATIONS_FEE) (/unique_chucks/15/0xbe138bb17d09a96166024e3f5b5cdff4c91d55dd.sol#197-198)

PreSale.setReached (/unique_chucks/15/0xbe138bb17d09a96166024e3f5b5cdff4c91d55dd.sol) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-token.transfer(owner,totalSupply) (/unique_chucks/15/0xbe138bb17d09a96166024e3f5b5cdff4c91d55dd.sol)

PreSale.MIN_AMOUNT should be constant (/unique_chucks/15/0xbe138bb17d09a96166024e3f5b5cdff4c91d55dd.sol#144-145)
PreSale.OPERATIONS_FEE should be constant (/unique_chucks/15/0xbe138bb17d09a96166024e3f5b5cdff4c91d55dd.sol#145-146)
PreSale.REF_BONUS_PERCENT should be constant (/unique_chucks/15/0xbe138bb17d09a96166024e3f5b5cdff4c91d55dd.sol#143-144)
PreSale.confirmTime should be constant (/unique_chucks/15/0xbe138bb17d09a96166024e3f5b5cdff4c91d55dd.sol#149-151)
